    dc:description "Fig. 2. MML-PV-42. Drawings (left) and pictures (right) of the right maxilla in A, lateral view; B, medial view; C, oclusal view. Abbreviations: ap, ascendent process; fwm, false wear marks; jf, jugal facet; mf, maxillary foramen; pf, palatine facet; rar, rugose anterior region; sd, secondary dentine; sdf, secondary dentine fork point; ur, upper ridge; Scale bar: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4712762/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

